metadata.name: Confident
metadata.description: "Confident" is a mash up of a selection of my original watercolour paintings which are combined to paint the womanâ€™s history. Each painting within the mash up portrays a different emotion. The paintings layered into this piece stem from the emotional experience I was living through at the time. "Confident" shows a woman layered with empowerment, sensuality, confidence and calm. There is also a self portrait hidden within.
